  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dd0\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dda \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2 12\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0ddb\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0d8b\u0db4\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dab-\u0d96\u0dc2\u0db0 \u0dc3\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Medical equipment worth 12 lakhs stolen from the President's residence",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that the people who had forcibly entered the Fort President's House attacked the medical center and stole medical equipment and medicines worth over 12 lakh rupees.",
        "This medical center is run by the Navy, and the Colombo Central Division Criminal Investigation Unit has started investigations in this regard, according to police sources.",
        "According to the police, the persons who entered the presidential palace entered the medical center and damaged the property and stole the stock of medical equipment and medicines stored there.",
        "The Navy has submitted this complaint to the police."
      ],
